5 years ago on our wedding day, a granthi gave us a meaningful speech on patience. He said, keep patience within yourself, patience with one another and above all, patience with Waheguru. In his time, no matter how difficult, you will receive all that is meant for you. 

This beautiful baby boy came into our lives when we least expected and needed him the most. Introducing our greatest blessing, Sabar Singh Pannu. Our little angel has brought so much happiness to our lives already 🤍🧸

Our family loves shopping at @freshcogrocery for all our ethnic groceries while keeping our budget in check. I use my Scene+ card for exclusive member pricing, earning and redeeming points for free groceries — 1000 points = $10 worth of groceries! This Vaisakhi, I’m preparing a special meal of Sholay (spiced chickpeas) and crispy, golden Poorian, a family favorite that brings back warm memories of festive celebrations. The rich, flavorful chickpeas paired with perfectly puffed Poorian make for the ultimate comfort food—symbolizing joy, togetherness, and the spirit of the harvest season. Wishing you all a Happy Vaisakhi from my family to yours!

Bring FreshCo home this Vaisakhi!
